An Antonov An-12 aircraft belonging to the Sudanese military crashes southwest of the capital Khartoum, killing at least 13 of the 22 people on board. (CNN) (Reuters)The drunken driver of a car, speeding at nearly 200 kilometre (124 miles) per hour, hits a bus stop on Minskaya Street in Moscow. Seven pedestrians who were waiting for the bus were killed. (Ria Novosti) (Xinhua)